import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap';

export const NavigationBar=()=> {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
      <LinkContainer to="/">
        <Navbar.Brand>Pics World</Navbar.Brand>
      </LinkContainer>
      <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav className="mr-auto">
          <LinkContainer to="/about">
            <Nav.Link>About</Nav.Link>
          </LinkContainer>
          <LinkContainer to="/contact">
            <Nav.Link>Contact</Nav.Link>
          </LinkContainer>
          <NavDropdown title="Dropdown" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
            <LinkContainer to="/dropdown/item1">
              <NavDropdown.Item>Item 1</NavDropdown.Item>
            </LinkContainer>
            <LinkContainer to="/dropdown/item2">
              <NavDropdown.Item>Item 2</NavDropdown.Item>
            </LinkContainer>
            <NavDropdown.Divider />
            <LinkContainer to="/dropdown/item3">
              <NavDropdown.Item>Item 3</NavDropdown.Item>
            </LinkContainer>
          </NavDropdown>
        </Nav>
      </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>
  );
}
